Routes from the far LEFT of the crag towards the right (i.e. back towards the car park) Vertical, 1 minute flat walk, Early morning shade & Late Afternoon shade This is one of Montagu's most popular crags due to the easier grade of routes and the 1 minute walk-in. Legoland is child friendly and dogs are allowed. Bosch Kloof Climbing Map There is no cellphone reception at any of these crags. Cell Phone Reception From Ashton/Cape Town direction: The large gravel parking area is just before the first bridge on the right. From Montagu direction: Drive towards Ashton/Cape Town, about 1km after the tunnel you will see the large gravel parking area on your left just over the bridge. How to get there You MUST park
